 124         @Override                                                                                        
 125         public void onReceive(Context context, Intent intent) {                                          
 126             String action = intent.getAction();                                                          
 127             if (action == null) {                                                                        
 128                 LOG.warn("no action");                                                                   
 129                 return;                                                                                  
 130             }                                                                                            
 131                                                                                                          
 132             int handle = (int) intent.getLongExtra("handle", -1);                                        
 133             switch (action) {                                                                            
 134                 case GBApplication.ACTION_QUIT:                                                          
 135                     stopSelf();                                                                          
 136                     break;                                                                               
 137                                                                                                          
 138                 case ACTION_OPEN: {                                                                      
 139                     StatusBarNotification[] sbns = NotificationListener.this.getActiveNotifications();   
 140                     Long ts = (Long) mNotificationHandleLookup.lookup(handle);                           
 141                     if (ts == null) {                                                                    
 142                         LOG.info("could not lookup handle for open action");                             
 143                         break;                                                                           
 144                     }                                                                                    
 145                                                                                                          
 146                     for (StatusBarNotification sbn : sbns) {                                             
 147                         if (sbn.getPostTime() == ts) {                                                   
 148                             try {                                                                        
 149                                 PendingIntent pi = sbn.getNotification().contentIntent;                  
 150                                 if (pi != null) {                                                        
 151                                     pi.send();                                                           
 152                                 }                                                                        
 153                             } catch (PendingIntent.CanceledException e) {                                
 154                                 e.printStackTrace();                                                     
 155                             }                                                                            
 156                         }                                                                                
 157                     }                                                                                    
 158                     break;                                                                               
 159                 }                                                                                        
 160                 case ACTION_MUTE:                                                                        
 161                     String packageName = (String) mPackageLookup.lookup(handle);                         
 162                     if (packageName == null) {                                                           
 163                         LOG.info("could not lookup handle for mute action");                             
 164                         break;                                                                           
 165                     }                                                                                    
 166                                                                                                          
 167                     LOG.info("going to mute " + packageName);                                            
 168                     GBApplication.addAppToNotifBlacklist(packageName);                                   
 169                     break;                                                                               
 170                 case ACTION_DISMISS: {                                                                   
 171                     StatusBarNotification[] sbns = NotificationListener.this.getActiveNotifications();   
 172                     Long ts = (Long) mNotificationHandleLookup.lookup(handle);                           
 173                     if (ts == null) {                                                                    
 174                         LOG.info("could not lookup handle for dismiss action");                          
 175                         break;                                                                           
 176                     }                                                                                    
 177                     for (StatusBarNotification sbn : sbns) {                                             
 178                         if (sbn.getPostTime() == ts) {                                                   
 179                             if (GBApplication.isRunningLollipopOrLater()) {                              
 180                                 String key = sbn.getKey();                                               
 181                                 NotificationListener.this.cancelNotification(key);                       
 182                             } else {                                                                     
 183                                 int id = sbn.getId();                                                    
 184                                 String pkg = sbn.getPackageName();                                       
 185                                 String tag = sbn.getTag();                                               
 186                                 NotificationListener.this.cancelNotification(pkg, tag, id);              
 187                             }                                                                            
 188                         }                                                                                
 189                     }                                                                                    
 190                     break;                                                                               
 191                 }                                                                                        
 192                 case ACTION_DISMISS_ALL:                                                                 
 193                     NotificationListener.this.cancelAllNotifications();                                  
 194                     break;                                                                               
 195                 case ACTION_REPLY:                                                                       
 196                     NotificationCompat.Action wearableAction = (NotificationCompat.Action) mActionLookup.🔵
 197                     String reply = intent.getStringExtra("reply");                                       
 198                     if (wearableAction != null) {                                                        
 199                         PendingIntent actionIntent = wearableAction.getActionIntent();                   
 200                         Intent localIntent = new Intent();                                               
 201                         localIntent.addFlags(Intent.FLAG_ACTIVITY_NEW_TASK);                             
 202                         if(wearableAction.getRemoteInputs()!=null) {                                     
 203                             RemoteInput[] remoteInputs = wearableAction.getRemoteInputs();               
 204                             Bundle extras = new Bundle();                                                
 205                             extras.putCharSequence(remoteInputs[0].getResultKey(), reply);               
 206                             RemoteInput.addResultsToIntent(remoteInputs, localIntent, extras);           
 207                         }                                                                                
 208                         try {                                                                            
 209                             LOG.info("will send exec intent to remote application");                     
 210                             actionIntent.send(context, 0, localIntent);                                  
 211                             mActionLookup.remove(handle);                                                
 212                         } catch (PendingIntent.CanceledException e) {                                    
 213                             LOG.warn("replyToLastNotification error: " + e.getLocalizedMessage());       
 214                         }                                                                                
 215                     }                                                                                    
 216                     break;                                                                               
 217             }                                                                                            
 218         }                                                                                                
 219     };

 446     private boolean checkNotificationContentForWhiteAndBlackList(String packageName, String body) {      
 447         long start = System.currentTimeMillis();                                                         
 448                                                                                                          
 449         List<String> wordsList = new ArrayList<>();                                                      
 450         NotificationFilter notificationFilter;                                                           
 451                                                                                                          
 452         try (DBHandler db = GBApplication.acquireDB()) {                                                 
 453                                                                                                          
 454             NotificationFilterDao notificationFilterDao = db.getDaoSession().getNotificationFilterDao(); 
 455             NotificationFilterEntryDao notificationFilterEntryDao = db.getDaoSession().getNotificationFil🔵
 456                                                                                                          
 457             Query<NotificationFilter> query = notificationFilterDao.queryBuilder().where(NotificationFilt🔵
 458             notificationFilter = query.unique();                                                         
 459                                                                                                          
 460             if (notificationFilter == null) {                                                            
 461                 LOG.debug("No Notification Filter found");                                               
 462                 return true;                                                                             
 463             }                                                                                            
 464                                                                                                          
 465             LOG.debug("Loaded notification filter for '{}'", packageName);                               
 466             Query<NotificationFilterEntry> queryEntries = notificationFilterEntryDao.queryBuilder().where🔵
 467                                                                                                          
 468             List<NotificationFilterEntry> filterEntries = queryEntries.list();                           
 469                                                                                                          
 470             if (BuildConfig.DEBUG) {                                                                     
 471                 LOG.info("Database lookup took '{}' ms", System.currentTimeMillis() - start);            
 472             }                                                                                            
 473                                                                                                          
 474             if (!filterEntries.isEmpty()) {                                                              
 475                 for (NotificationFilterEntry temp : filterEntries) {                                     
 476                     wordsList.add(temp.getNotificationFilterContent());                                  
 477                     LOG.debug("Loaded filter word: " + temp.getNotificationFilterContent());             
 478                 }                                                                                        
 479             }                                                                                            
 480                                                                                                          
 481         } catch (Exception e) {                                                                          
 482             LOG.error("Could not acquire DB.", e);                                                       
 483             return true;                                                                                 
 484         }                                                                                                
 485                                                                                                          
 486         return shouldContinueAfterFilter(body, wordsList, notificationFilter);                           
 487     }

 489     private void handleCallNotification(StatusBarNotification sbn) {                                     
 490         String app = sbn.getPackageName();                                                               
 491         LOG.debug("got call from: " + app);                                                              
 492         if(app.equals("com.android.dialer")) {                                                           
 493             LOG.debug("Ignoring non-voip call");                                                         
 494             return;                                                                                      
 495         }                                                                                                
 496         Notification noti = sbn.getNotification();                                                       
 497         dumpExtras(noti.extras);

 529             number = appName != null ? appName : app;

 574                     LOG.info("Every word was found, whitelist has effect, processing continues.");

 591     // Strip Unicode control sequences: some apps like Telegram add a lot of them for unknown reasons    
 592     private String sanitizeUnicode(String orig) {                                                        
 593         return orig.replaceAll("\\p{C}", "");                                                            
 594     }

 596     private void dissectNotificationTo(Notification notification, NotificationSpec notificationSpec,     
 597                                        boolean preferBigText) {                                          
 598                                                                                                          
 599         Bundle extras = NotificationCompat.getExtras(notification);                                      
 600                                                                                                          
 601         //dumpExtras(extras);                                                                            
 602         if (extras == null) {                                                                            
 603             return;                                                                                      
 604         }                                                                                                
 605                                                                                                          
 606         CharSequence title = extras.getCharSequence(Notification.EXTRA_TITLE);                           
 607         if (title != null) {                                                                             
 608             notificationSpec.title = sanitizeUnicode(title.toString());                                  
 609         }                                                                                                
 610                                                                                                          
 611         CharSequence contentCS = null;                                                                   
 612         if (preferBigText && extras.containsKey(Notification.EXTRA_BIG_TEXT)) {                          
 613             contentCS = extras.getCharSequence(NotificationCompat.EXTRA_BIG_TEXT);                       
 614         } else if (extras.containsKey(Notification.EXTRA_TEXT)) {                                        
 615             contentCS = extras.getCharSequence(NotificationCompat.EXTRA_TEXT);                           
 616         }                                                                                                
 617         if (contentCS != null) {                                                                         
 618             notificationSpec.body = sanitizeUnicode(contentCS.toString());                               
 619         }                                                                                                
 620                                                                                                          
 621     }

 623     private boolean isServiceRunning() {                                                                 
 624         ActivityManager manager = (ActivityManager) getSystemService(ACTIVITY_SERVICE);                  
 625         if (manager == null) {                                                                           
 626             return false;                                                                                
 627         }                                                                                                
 628         for (ActivityManager.RunningServiceInfo service : manager.getRunningServices(Integer.MAX_VALUE)) 🔵
 629             if (DeviceCommunicationService.class.getName().equals(service.service.getClassName())) {     
 630                 return true;                                                                             
 631             }                                                                                            
 632         }                                                                                                
 633         return false;                                                                                    
 634     }

 641     /**                                                                                                  
 642      * Try to handle media session notifications that tell info about the current play state.            
 643      *                                                                                                   
 644      * @param mediaSession The mediasession to handle.                                                   
 645      * @return true if notification was handled, false otherwise                                         
 646      */                                                                                                  
 647     public boolean handleMediaSessionNotification(MediaSessionCompat.Token mediaSession) {               
 648         MusicSpec musicSpec = new MusicSpec();                                                           
 649         MusicStateSpec stateSpec = new MusicStateSpec();                                                 
 650                                                                                                          
 651         MediaControllerCompat c;                                                                         
 652         try {                                                                                            
 653             c = new MediaControllerCompat(getApplicationContext(), mediaSession);                        
 654                                                                                                          
 655             PlaybackStateCompat s = c.getPlaybackState();                                                
 656             stateSpec.position = (int) (s.getPosition() / 1000);                                         
 657             stateSpec.playRate = Math.round(100 * s.getPlaybackSpeed());                                 
 658             stateSpec.repeat = 1;                                                                        
 659             stateSpec.shuffle = 1;                                                                       
 660             switch (s.getState()) {                                                                      
 661                 case PlaybackStateCompat.STATE_PLAYING:                                                  
 662                     stateSpec.state = MusicStateSpec.STATE_PLAYING;                                      
 663                     break;                                                                               
 664                 case PlaybackStateCompat.STATE_STOPPED:                                                  
 665                     stateSpec.state = MusicStateSpec.STATE_STOPPED;                                      
 666                     break;                                                                               
 667                 case PlaybackStateCompat.STATE_PAUSED:                                                   
 668                     stateSpec.state = MusicStateSpec.STATE_PAUSED;                                       
 669                     break;                                                                               
 670                 default:                                                                                 
 671                     stateSpec.state = MusicStateSpec.STATE_UNKNOWN;                                      
 672                     break;                                                                               
 673             }                                                                                            
 674                                                                                                          
 675             MediaMetadataCompat d = c.getMetadata();                                                     
 676             if (d == null)                                                                               
 677                 return false;                                                                            
 678             if (d.containsKey(MediaMetadata.METADATA_KEY_ARTIST))                                        
 679                 musicSpec.artist = d.getString(MediaMetadataCompat.METADATA_KEY_ARTIST);                 
 680             if (d.containsKey(MediaMetadata.METADATA_KEY_ALBUM))                                         
 681                 musicSpec.album = d.getString(MediaMetadataCompat.METADATA_KEY_ALBUM);                   
 682             if (d.containsKey(MediaMetadata.METADATA_KEY_TITLE))                                         
 683                 musicSpec.track = d.getString(MediaMetadataCompat.METADATA_KEY_TITLE);                   
 684             if (d.containsKey(MediaMetadata.METADATA_KEY_DURATION))                                      
 685                 musicSpec.duration = (int) d.getLong(MediaMetadataCompat.METADATA_KEY_DURATION) / 1000;  
 686             if (d.containsKey(MediaMetadata.METADATA_KEY_NUM_TRACKS))                                    
 687                 musicSpec.trackCount = (int) d.getLong(MediaMetadataCompat.METADATA_KEY_NUM_TRACKS);     
 688             if (d.containsKey(MediaMetadata.METADATA_KEY_TRACK_NUMBER))                                  
 689                 musicSpec.trackNr = (int) d.getLong(MediaMetadataCompat.METADATA_KEY_TRACK_NUMBER);      
 690                                                                                                          
 691             // finally, tell the device about it                                                         
 692             GBApplication.deviceService().onSetMusicInfo(musicSpec);                                     
 693             GBApplication.deviceService().onSetMusicState(stateSpec);                                    
 694                                                                                                          
 695             return true;                                                                                 
 696         } catch (NullPointerException | RemoteException e) {                                             
 697             return false;                                                                                
 698         }                                                                                                
 699     }

 702     public void onNotificationRemoved(StatusBarNotification sbn) {                                       
 703         logNotification(sbn, false);                                                                     
 704                                                                                                          
 705         notificationStack.remove(sbn.getPackageName());                                                  
 706                                                                                                          
 707         if (shouldIgnoreNotifications()) return;                                                         
 708         if (shouldIgnoreSource(sbn)) return;                                                             
 709                                                                                                          
 710         if (handleMediaSessionNotification(sbn)) return;                                                 
 711                                                                                                          
 712         if (GBApplication.isRunningLollipopOrLater()) {                                                  
 713             if(Notification.CATEGORY_CALL.equals(sbn.getNotification().category)                         
 714                     && activeCallPostTime == sbn.getPostTime()) {                                        
 715                 activeCallPostTime = 0;                                                                  
 716                 CallSpec callSpec = new CallSpec();                                                      
 717                 callSpec.command = CallSpec.CALL_END;                                                    
 718                 mLastCallCommand = callSpec.command;                                                     
 719                 GBApplication.deviceService().onSetCallState(callSpec);                                  
 720             }                                                                                            
 721         }                                                                                                
 722         // FIXME: DISABLED for now                                                                       
 723                                                                                                          
 724         if (shouldIgnoreNotification(sbn)) return;                                                       
 725                                                                                                          
 726         Prefs prefs = GBApplication.getPrefs();                                                          
 727         if (prefs.getBoolean("autoremove_notifications", true)) {                                        
 728             LOG.info("notification removed, will ask device to delete it");                              
 729             GBApplication.deviceService().onDeleteNotification((int) sbn.getPostTime());                 
 730         }                                                                                                
 731                                                                                                          
 732     }

 123                                                                                                          
 124         @Override                                                                                        
 125         public void onReceive(Context context, Intent intent) {                                          
 126             String action = intent.getAction();                                                          
 127             if (action == null) {                                                                        
 128                 LOG.warn("no action");                                                                   
 129                 return;                                                                                  
 130             }                                                                                            
 131                                                                                                          
 132             int handle = (int) intent.getLongExtra("handle", -1);                                        
 133             switch (action) {                                                                            
 134                 case GBApplication.ACTION_QUIT:                                                          
 135                     stopSelf();                                                                          
 136                     break;                                                                               
 137                                                                                                          
 138                 case ACTION_OPEN: {                                                                      
 139                     StatusBarNotification[] sbns = NotificationListener.this.getActiveNotifications();   
 140                     Long ts = (Long) mNotificationHandleLookup.lookup(handle);                           
 141                     if (ts == null) {                                                                    
 142                         LOG.info("could not lookup handle for open action");                             
 143                         break;                                                                           
 144                     }                                                                                    
 145                                                                                                          
 146                     for (StatusBarNotification sbn : sbns) {                                             
 147                         if (sbn.getPostTime() == ts) {                                                   
 148                             try {                                                                        
 149                                 PendingIntent pi = sbn.getNotification().contentIntent;                  
 150                                 if (pi != null) {                                                        
 151                                     pi.send();                                                           
 152                                 }                                                                        
 153                             } catch (PendingIntent.CanceledException e) {                                
 154                                 e.printStackTrace();                                                     
 155                             }                                                                            
 156                         }                                                                                
 157                     }                                                                                    
 158                     break;                                                                               
 159                 }                                                                                        
 160                 case ACTION_MUTE:                                                                        
 161                     String packageName = (String) mPackageLookup.lookup(handle);                         
 162                     if (packageName == null) {                                                           
 163                         LOG.info("could not lookup handle for mute action");                             
 164                         break;                                                                           
 165                     }                                                                                    
 166                                                                                                          
 167                     LOG.info("going to mute " + packageName);                                            
 168                     GBApplication.addAppToNotifBlacklist(packageName);                                   
 169                     break;                                                                               
 170                 case ACTION_DISMISS: {                                                                   
 171                     StatusBarNotification[] sbns = NotificationListener.this.getActiveNotifications();   
 172                     Long ts = (Long) mNotificationHandleLookup.lookup(handle);                           
 173                     if (ts == null) {                                                                    
 174                         LOG.info("could not lookup handle for dismiss action");                          
 175                         break;                                                                           
 176                     }                                                                                    
 177                     for (StatusBarNotification sbn : sbns) {                                             
 178                         if (sbn.getPostTime() == ts) {                                                   
 179                             if (GBApplication.isRunningLollipopOrLater()) {                              
 180                                 String key = sbn.getKey();                                               
 181                                 NotificationListener.this.cancelNotification(key);                       
 182                             } else {                                                                     
 183                                 int id = sbn.getId();                                                    
 184                                 String pkg = sbn.getPackageName();                                       
 185                                 String tag = sbn.getTag();                                               
 186                                 NotificationListener.this.cancelNotification(pkg, tag, id);              
 187                             }                                                                            
 188                         }                                                                                
 189                     }                                                                                    
 190                     break;                                                                               
 191                 }                                                                                        
 192                 case ACTION_DISMISS_ALL:                                                                 
 193                     NotificationListener.this.cancelAllNotifications();                                  
 194                     break;                                                                               
 195                 case ACTION_REPLY:                                                                       
 196                     NotificationCompat.Action wearableAction = (NotificationCompat.Action) mActionLookup.🔵
 197                     String reply = intent.getStringExtra("reply");                                       
 198                     if (wearableAction != null) {                                                        
 199                         PendingIntent actionIntent = wearableAction.getActionIntent();                   
 200                         Intent localIntent = new Intent();                                               
 201                         localIntent.addFlags(Intent.FLAG_ACTIVITY_NEW_TASK);                             
 202                         if(wearableAction.getRemoteInputs()!=null) {                                     
 203                             RemoteInput[] remoteInputs = wearableAction.getRemoteInputs();               
 204                             Bundle extras = new Bundle();                                                
 205                             extras.putCharSequence(remoteInputs[0].getResultKey(), reply);               
 206                             RemoteInput.addResultsToIntent(remoteInputs, localIntent, extras);           
 207                         }                                                                                
 208                         try {                                                                            
 209                             LOG.info("will send exec intent to remote application");                     
 210                             actionIntent.send(context, 0, localIntent);                                  
 211                             mActionLookup.remove(handle);                                                
 212                         } catch (PendingIntent.CanceledException e) {                                    
 213                             LOG.warn("replyToLastNotification error: " + e.getLocalizedMessage());       
 214                         }                                                                                
 215                     }                                                                                    
 216                     break;                                                                               
 217             }                                                                                            
 218         }                                                                                                
 219     };

 221     @Override                                                                                            
 222     public void onCreate() {                                                                             
 223         super.onCreate();                                                                                
 224         IntentFilter filterLocal = new IntentFilter();                                                   
 225         filterLocal.addAction(GBApplication.ACTION_QUIT);                                                
 226         filterLocal.addAction(ACTION_OPEN);                                                              
 227         filterLocal.addAction(ACTION_DISMISS);                                                           
 228         filterLocal.addAction(ACTION_DISMISS_ALL);                                                       
 229         filterLocal.addAction(ACTION_MUTE);                                                              
 230         filterLocal.addAction(ACTION_REPLY);                                                             
 231         LocalBroadcastManager.getInstance(this).registerReceiver(mReceiver, filterLocal);                
 232     }

 236         LocalBroadcastManager.getInstance(this).unregisterReceiver(mReceiver);                           
 237         notificationStack.clear();                                                                       
 238         super.onDestroy();

 443     private boolean checkNotificationContentForWhiteAndBlackList(String packageName, String body) {      
 444         long start = System.currentTimeMillis();                                                         
 445                                                                                                          
 446         List<String> wordsList = new ArrayList<>();                                                      
 447         NotificationFilter notificationFilter;                                                           
 448                                                                                                          
 449         try (DBHandler db = GBApplication.acquireDB()) {                                                 
 450                                                                                                          
 451             NotificationFilterDao notificationFilterDao = db.getDaoSession().getNotificationFilterDao(); 
 452             NotificationFilterEntryDao notificationFilterEntryDao = db.getDaoSession().getNotificationFil🔵
 453                                                                                                          
 454             Query<NotificationFilter> query = notificationFilterDao.queryBuilder().where(NotificationFilt🔵
 455             notificationFilter = query.unique();                                                         
 456                                                                                                          
 457             if (notificationFilter == null) {                                                            
 458                 LOG.debug("No Notification Filter found");                                               
 459                 return true;                                                                             
 460             }                                                                                            
 461                                                                                                          
 462             LOG.debug("Loaded notification filter for '{}'", packageName);                               
 463             Query<NotificationFilterEntry> queryEntries = notificationFilterEntryDao.queryBuilder().where🔵
 464                                                                                                          
 465             List<NotificationFilterEntry> filterEntries = queryEntries.list();                           
 466                                                                                                          
 467             if (BuildConfig.DEBUG) {                                                                     
 468                 LOG.info("Database lookup took '{}' ms", System.currentTimeMillis() - start);            
 469             }                                                                                            
 470                                                                                                          
 471             if (!filterEntries.isEmpty()) {                                                              
 472                 for (NotificationFilterEntry temp : filterEntries) {                                     
 473                     wordsList.add(temp.getNotificationFilterContent());                                  
 474                     LOG.debug("Loaded filter word: " + temp.getNotificationFilterContent());             
 475                 }                                                                                        
 476             }                                                                                            
 477                                                                                                          
 478         } catch (Exception e) {                                                                          
 479             LOG.error("Could not acquire DB.", e);                                                       
 480             return true;                                                                                 
 481         }                                                                                                
 482                                                                                                          
 483         return shouldContinueAfterFilter(body, wordsList, notificationFilter);                           
 484     }

 486     private void handleCallNotification(StatusBarNotification sbn) {                                     
 487         String app = sbn.getPackageName();                                                               
 488         LOG.debug("got call from: " + app);                                                              
 489         if(app.equals("com.android.dialer")) {                                                           
 490             LOG.debug("Ignoring non-voip call");                                                         
 491             return;                                                                                      
 492         }                                                                                                
 493         Notification noti = sbn.getNotification();                                                       
 494         dumpExtras(noti.extras);                                                                         
 495         boolean callStarted = false;                                                                     
 496         if(noti.actions != null && noti.actions.length > 0) {                                            
 497             for (Notification.Action action : noti.actions) {                                            
 498                 LOG.info("Found call action: " + action.title);                                          
 499             }                                                                                            
 500             if (noti.actions.length == 1) {                                                              
 501                 if (mLastCallCommand == CallSpec.CALL_INCOMING) {                                        
 502                     LOG.info("There is only one call action and previous state was CALL_INCOMING, assumin🔵
 503                     callStarted = true;                                                                  
 504                 } else {                                                                                 
 505                     LOG.info("There is only one call action and previous state was not CALL_INCOMING, ass🔵
 506                     // FIXME: is there a way to detect transition CALL_OUTGOING -> CALL_START for more co🔵
 507                     return;                                                                              
 508                 }                                                                                        
 509             }                                                                                            
 510             /*try {                                                                                      
 511                 LOG.info("Executing first action");                                                      
 512                 noti.actions[0].actionIntent.send();                                                     
 513             } catch (PendingIntent.CanceledException e) {                                                
 514                 e.printStackTrace();                                                                     
 515             }*/                                                                                          
 516         }                                                                                                
 517                                                                                                          
 518         // figure out sender                                                                             
 519         String number;                                                                                   
 520         if(noti.extras.containsKey(Notification.EXTRA_PEOPLE)) {                                         
 521             number = noti.extras.getString(Notification.EXTRA_PEOPLE);                                   
 522         } else if(noti.extras.containsKey(Notification.EXTRA_TITLE)) {                                   
 523             number = noti.extras.getString(Notification.EXTRA_TITLE);                                    
 524         } else {                                                                                         
 525             String appName = getAppName(app);                                                            
 526             number = appName != null ? appName : app;                                                    
 527         }                                                                                                
 528         activeCallPostTime = sbn.getPostTime();

 532         mLastCallCommand = callSpec.command;                                                             
 533         GBApplication.deviceService().onSetCallState(callSpec);

 536     boolean shouldContinueAfterFilter(@NonNull String body, @NonNull List<String> wordsList, @NonNull Not🔵
 537                                                                                                          
 538         LOG.debug("Mode: '{}' Submode: '{}' WordsList: '{}'", notificationFilter.getNotificationFilterMod🔵
 539                                                                                                          
 540         boolean allMode = notificationFilter.getNotificationFilterSubMode() == NOTIFICATION_FILTER_SUBMOD🔵
 541                                                                                                          
 542         switch (notificationFilter.getNotificationFilterMode()) {                                        
 543             case NOTIFICATION_FILTER_MODE_BLACKLIST:                                                     
 544                 if (allMode) {                                                                           
 545                     for (String word : wordsList) {                                                      
 546                         if (!body.contains(word)) {                                                      
 547                             LOG.info("Not every word was found, blacklist has no effect, processing conti🔵
 548                             return true;                                                                 
 549                         }                                                                                
 550                     }                                                                                    
 551                     LOG.info("Every word was found, blacklist has effect, processing stops.");           
 552                     return false;                                                                        
 553                 } else {                                                                                 
 554                     boolean containsAny = StringUtils.containsAny(body, wordsList.toArray(new CharSequenc🔵
 555                     if (!containsAny) {                                                                  
 556                         LOG.info("No matching word was found, blacklist has no effect, processing continu🔵
 557                     } else {                                                                             
 558                         LOG.info("At least one matching word was found, blacklist has effect, processing 🔵
 559                     }                                                                                    
 560                     return !containsAny;                                                                 
 561                 }                                                                                        
 562                                                                                                          
 563             case NOTIFICATION_FILTER_MODE_WHITELIST:                                                     
 564                 if (allMode) {                                                                           
 565                     for (String word : wordsList) {                                                      
 566                         if (!body.contains(word)) {                                                      
 567                             LOG.info("Not every word was found, whitelist has no effect, processing stops🔵
 568                             return false;                                                                
 569                         }                                                                                
 570                     }                                                                                    
 571                     LOG.info("Every word was found, whitelist has effect, processing continues.");       
 572                     return true;                                                                         
 573                 } else {                                                                                 
 574                     boolean containsAny = StringUtils.containsAny(body, wordsList.toArray(new CharSequenc🔵
 575                     if (containsAny) {                                                                   
 576                         LOG.info("At least one matching word was found, whitelist has effect, processing 🔵
 577                     } else {                                                                             
 578                         LOG.info("No matching word was found, whitelist has no effect, processing stops."🔵
 579                     }                                                                                    
 580                     return containsAny;                                                                  
 581                 }                                                                                        
 582                                                                                                          
 583             default:                                                                                     
 584                 return true;                                                                             
 585         }                                                                                                
 586     }

 588     // Strip Unicode control sequences: some apps like Telegram add a lot of them for unknown reasons    
 589     private String sanitizeUnicode(String orig) {                                                        
 590         return orig.replaceAll("\\p{C}", "");                                                            
 591     }

 593     private void dissectNotificationTo(Notification notification, NotificationSpec notificationSpec,     
 594                                        boolean preferBigText) {                                          
 595                                                                                                          
 596         Bundle extras = NotificationCompat.getExtras(notification);                                      
 597                                                                                                          
 598         //dumpExtras(extras);                                                                            
 599         if (extras == null) {                                                                            
 600             return;                                                                                      
 601         }                                                                                                
 602                                                                                                          
 603         CharSequence title = extras.getCharSequence(Notification.EXTRA_TITLE);                           
 604         if (title != null) {                                                                             
 605             notificationSpec.title = sanitizeUnicode(title.toString());                                  
 606         }                                                                                                
 607                                                                                                          
 608         CharSequence contentCS = null;                                                                   
 609         if (preferBigText && extras.containsKey(Notification.EXTRA_BIG_TEXT)) {                          
 610             contentCS = extras.getCharSequence(NotificationCompat.EXTRA_BIG_TEXT);                       
 611         } else if (extras.containsKey(Notification.EXTRA_TEXT)) {                                        
 612             contentCS = extras.getCharSequence(NotificationCompat.EXTRA_TEXT);                           
 613         }                                                                                                
 614         if (contentCS != null) {                                                                         
 615             notificationSpec.body = sanitizeUnicode(contentCS.toString());                               
 616         }                                                                                                
 617                                                                                                          
 618     }

 620     private boolean isServiceRunning() {                                                                 
 621         ActivityManager manager = (ActivityManager) getSystemService(ACTIVITY_SERVICE);                  
 622         if (manager == null) {                                                                           
 623             return false;                                                                                
 624         }                                                                                                
 625         for (ActivityManager.RunningServiceInfo service : manager.getRunningServices(Integer.MAX_VALUE)) 🔵
 626             if (DeviceCommunicationService.class.getName().equals(service.service.getClassName())) {     
 627                 return true;                                                                             
 628             }                                                                                            
 629         }                                                                                                
 630         return false;                                                                                    
 631     }

 635         return mediaSession != null && handleMediaSessionNotification(mediaSession);

 638     /**                                                                                                  
 639      * Try to handle media session notifications that tell info about the current play state.            
 640      *                                                                                                   
 641      * @param mediaSession The mediasession to handle.                                                   
 642      * @return true if notification was handled, false otherwise                                         
 643      */                                                                                                  
 644     public boolean handleMediaSessionNotification(MediaSessionCompat.Token mediaSession) {               
 645         MusicSpec musicSpec = new MusicSpec();                                                           
 646         MusicStateSpec stateSpec = new MusicStateSpec();                                                 
 647                                                                                                          
 648         MediaControllerCompat c;                                                                         
 649         try {                                                                                            
 650             c = new MediaControllerCompat(getApplicationContext(), mediaSession);                        
 651                                                                                                          
 652             PlaybackStateCompat s = c.getPlaybackState();                                                
 653             stateSpec.position = (int) (s.getPosition() / 1000);                                         
 654             stateSpec.playRate = Math.round(100 * s.getPlaybackSpeed());                                 
 655             stateSpec.repeat = 1;                                                                        
 656             stateSpec.shuffle = 1;                                                                       
 657             switch (s.getState()) {                                                                      
 658                 case PlaybackStateCompat.STATE_PLAYING:                                                  
 659                     stateSpec.state = MusicStateSpec.STATE_PLAYING;                                      
 660                     break;                                                                               
 661                 case PlaybackStateCompat.STATE_STOPPED:                                                  
 662                     stateSpec.state = MusicStateSpec.STATE_STOPPED;                                      
 663                     break;                                                                               
 664                 case PlaybackStateCompat.STATE_PAUSED:                                                   
 665                     stateSpec.state = MusicStateSpec.STATE_PAUSED;                                       
 666                     break;                                                                               
 667                 default:                                                                                 
 668                     stateSpec.state = MusicStateSpec.STATE_UNKNOWN;                                      
 669                     break;                                                                               
 670             }                                                                                            
 671                                                                                                          
 672             MediaMetadataCompat d = c.getMetadata();                                                     
 673             if (d == null)                                                                               
 674                 return false;                                                                            
 675             if (d.containsKey(MediaMetadata.METADATA_KEY_ARTIST))                                        
 676                 musicSpec.artist = d.getString(MediaMetadataCompat.METADATA_KEY_ARTIST);                 
 677             if (d.containsKey(MediaMetadata.METADATA_KEY_ALBUM))                                         
 678                 musicSpec.album = d.getString(MediaMetadataCompat.METADATA_KEY_ALBUM);                   
 679             if (d.containsKey(MediaMetadata.METADATA_KEY_TITLE))                                         
 680                 musicSpec.track = d.getString(MediaMetadataCompat.METADATA_KEY_TITLE);                   
 681             if (d.containsKey(MediaMetadata.METADATA_KEY_DURATION))                                      
 682                 musicSpec.duration = (int) d.getLong(MediaMetadataCompat.METADATA_KEY_DURATION) / 1000;  
 683             if (d.containsKey(MediaMetadata.METADATA_KEY_NUM_TRACKS))                                    
 684                 musicSpec.trackCount = (int) d.getLong(MediaMetadataCompat.METADATA_KEY_NUM_TRACKS);     
 685             if (d.containsKey(MediaMetadata.METADATA_KEY_TRACK_NUMBER))                                  
 686                 musicSpec.trackNr = (int) d.getLong(MediaMetadataCompat.METADATA_KEY_TRACK_NUMBER);      
 687                                                                                                          
 688             // finally, tell the device about it                                                         
 689             GBApplication.deviceService().onSetMusicInfo(musicSpec);                                     
 690             GBApplication.deviceService().onSetMusicState(stateSpec);                                    
 691                                                                                                          
 692             return true;                                                                                 
 693         } catch (NullPointerException | RemoteException e) {                                             
 694             return false;                                                                                
 695         }                                                                                                
 696     }

 699     public void onNotificationRemoved(StatusBarNotification sbn) {                                       
 700         logNotification(sbn, false);                                                                     
 701                                                                                                          
 702         notificationStack.remove(sbn.getPackageName());                                                  
 703                                                                                                          
 704         if (shouldIgnoreNotifications()) return;                                                         
 705         if (shouldIgnoreSource(sbn)) return;                                                             
 706                                                                                                          
 707         if (handleMediaSessionNotification(sbn)) return;                                                 
 708                                                                                                          
 709         if (GBApplication.isRunningLollipopOrLater()) {                                                  
 710             if(Notification.CATEGORY_CALL.equals(sbn.getNotification().category)                         
 711                     && activeCallPostTime == sbn.getPostTime()) {                                        
 712             activeCallPostTime = 0;                                                                      
 713             CallSpec callSpec = new CallSpec();                                                          
 714             callSpec.command = CallSpec.CALL_END;                                                        
 715                 mLastCallCommand = callSpec.command;                                                     
 716             GBApplication.deviceService().onSetCallState(callSpec);                                      
 717         }                                                                                                
 718         }                                                                                                
 719         // FIXME: DISABLED for now                                                                       
 720                                                                                                          
 721         if (shouldIgnoreNotification(sbn)) return;                                                       
 722                                                                                                          
 723         Prefs prefs = GBApplication.getPrefs();                                                          
 724         if (prefs.getBoolean("autoremove_notifications", true)) {                                        
 725             LOG.info("notification removed, will ask device to delete it");                              
 726             GBApplication.deviceService().onDeleteNotification((int) sbn.getPostTime());                 
 727         }                                                                                                
 728                                                                                                          
 729     }

 886     /**                                                                                                  
 887      * Get the notification color that should be used for this Pebble notification.                      
 888      *                                                                                                   
 889      * Note that this method will *not* edit the NotificationSpec passed in. It will only evaluate the Pe🔵
 890      *                                                                                                   
 891      * See Issue #815 on GitHub to see how notification colors are set.                                  
 892      *                                                                                                   
 893      * @param notificationSpec The NotificationSpec to read from.                                        
 894      * @return Returns a PebbleColor that best represents this notification.                             
 895      */                                                                                                  
 896     private byte getPebbleColorForNotification(NotificationSpec notificationSpec) {                      
 897         String appId = notificationSpec.sourceAppId;                                                     
 898         NotificationType existingType = notificationSpec.type;                                           
 899                                                                                                          
 900         // If the notification type is known, return the associated color.                               
 901         if (existingType != NotificationType.UNKNOWN) {                                                  
 902             return existingType.color;                                                                   
 903         }                                                                                                
 904                                                                                                          
 905         // Otherwise, we go and attempt to find the color from the app icon.                             
 906         Drawable icon;                                                                                   
 907         try {                                                                                            
 908             icon = getApplicationContext().getPackageManager().getApplicationIcon(appId);                
 909             Objects.requireNonNull(icon);                                                                
 910         } catch (Exception ex) {                                                                         
 911             // If we can't get the icon, we go with the default defined above.                           
 912             LOG.warn("Could not get icon for AppID " + appId, ex);                                       
 913             return PebbleColor.IslamicGreen;                                                             
 914         }                                                                                                
 915                                                                                                          
 916         Bitmap bitmapIcon = BitmapUtil.convertDrawableToBitmap(icon);                                    
 917         int iconPrimaryColor = new Palette.Builder(bitmapIcon)                                           
 918                 .generate()                                                                              
 919                 .getVibrantColor(Color.parseColor("#aa0000"));                                           
 920                                                                                                          
 921         return PebbleUtils.getPebbleColor(iconPrimaryColor);                                             
 922     }
