 126         @Override                                                                                        
 127         public void onReceive(Context context, Intent intent) {                                          
 128             String action = intent.getAction();                                                          
 129             if (action == null) {                                                                        
 130                 LOG.warn("no action");                                                                   
 131                 return;                                                                                  
 132             }                                                                                            
 133             int handle = ((int) (intent.getLongExtra("handle", -1)));                                    
 134             switch (action) {                                                                            
 135                 case GBApplication.ACTION_QUIT :                                                         
 136                     stopSelf();                                                                          
 137                     break;                                                                               
 138                 case ACTION_OPEN :                                                                       
 139                     {                                                                                    
 140                         StatusBarNotification[] sbns = NotificationListener.this.getActiveNotifications()🔵
 141                         Long ts = ((Long) (mNotificationHandleLookup.lookup(handle)));                   
 142                         if (ts == null) {                                                                
 143                             LOG.info("could not lookup handle for open action");                         
 144                             break;                                                                       
 145                         }                                                                                
 146                         for (StatusBarNotification sbn : sbns) {                                         
 147                             if (sbn.getPostTime() == ts) {                                               
 148                                 try {                                                                    
 149                                     PendingIntent pi = sbn.getNotification().contentIntent;              
 150                                     if (pi != null) {                                                    
 151                                         pi.send();                                                       
 152                                     }                                                                    
 153                                 } catch (PendingIntent e) {                                              
 154                                     e.printStackTrace();                                                 
 155                                 }                                                                        
 156                             }                                                                            
 157                         }                                                                                
 158                         break;                                                                           
 159                     }                                                                                    
 160                 case ACTION_MUTE :                                                                       
 161                     String packageName = ((String) (mPackageLookup.lookup(handle)));                     
 162                     if (packageName == null) {                                                           
 163                         LOG.info("could not lookup handle for mute action");                             
 164                         break;                                                                           
 165                     }                                                                                    
 166                     LOG.info("going to mute " + packageName);                                            
 167                     GBApplication.addAppToNotifBlacklist(packageName);                                   
 168                     break;                                                                               
 169                 case ACTION_DISMISS :                                                                    
 170                     {                                                                                    
 171                         StatusBarNotification[] sbns = NotificationListener.this.getActiveNotifications()🔵
 172                         Long ts = ((Long) (mNotificationHandleLookup.lookup(handle)));                   
 173                         if (ts == null) {                                                                
 174                             LOG.info("could not lookup handle for dismiss action");                      
 175                             break;                                                                       
 176                         }                                                                                
 177                         for (StatusBarNotification sbn : sbns) {                                         
 178                             if (sbn.getPostTime() == ts) {                                               
 179                                 if (GBApplication.isRunningLollipopOrLater()) {                          
 180                                     String key = sbn.getKey();                                           
 181                                     NotificationListener.this.cancelNotification(key);                   
 182                                 } else {                                                                 
 183                                     int id = sbn.getId();                                                
 184                                     String pkg = sbn.getPackageName();                                   
 185                                     String tag = sbn.getTag();                                           
 186                                     NotificationListener.this.cancelNotification(pkg, tag, id);          
 187                                 }                                                                        
 188                             }                                                                            
 189                         }                                                                                
 190                         break;                                                                           
 191                     }                                                                                    
 192                 case ACTION_DISMISS_ALL :                                                                
 193                     NotificationListener.this.cancelAllNotifications();                                  
 194                     break;                                                                               
 195                 case ACTION_REPLY :                                                                      
 196                     NotificationCompat.Action wearableAction = ((NotificationCompat.Action) (mActionLooku🔵
 197                     String reply = intent.getStringExtra("reply");                                       
 198                     if (wearableAction != null) {                                                        
 199                         PendingIntent actionIntent = wearableAction.getActionIntent();                   
 200                         Intent localIntent = new Intent();                                               
 201                         localIntent.addFlags(Intent.FLAG_ACTIVITY_NEW_TASK);                             
 202                         if (wearableAction.getRemoteInputs() != null) {                                  
 203                             RemoteInput[] remoteInputs = wearableAction.getRemoteInputs();               
 204                             Bundle extras = new Bundle();                                                
 205                             extras.putCharSequence(remoteInputs[0].getResultKey(), reply);               
 206                             RemoteInput.addResultsToIntent(remoteInputs, localIntent, extras);           
 207                         }                                                                                
 208                         try {                                                                            
 209                             LOG.info("will send exec intent to remote application");                     
 210                             actionIntent.send(context, 0, localIntent);                                  
 211                             mActionLookup.remove(handle);                                                
 212                         } catch (PendingIntent e) {                                                      
 213                             LOG.warn("replyToLastNotification error: " + e.getLocalizedMessage());       
 214                         }                                                                                
 215                     }                                                                                    
 216                     break;                                                                               
 217             }                                                                                            
 218         }                                                                                                
 219     };

 439     private boolean checkNotificationContentForWhiteAndBlackList(String packageName, String body) {      
 440         long start = System.currentTimeMillis();                                                         
 441                                                                                                          
 442         List<String> wordsList = new ArrayList<>();                                                      
 443         NotificationFilter notificationFilter;                                                           
 444                                                                                                          
 445         try (DBHandler db = GBApplication.acquireDB()) {                                                 
 446                                                                                                          
 447             NotificationFilterDao notificationFilterDao = db.getDaoSession().getNotificationFilterDao(); 
 448             NotificationFilterEntryDao notificationFilterEntryDao = db.getDaoSession().getNotificationFil🔵
 449                                                                                                          
 450             Query<NotificationFilter> query = notificationFilterDao.queryBuilder().where(NotificationFilt🔵
 451             notificationFilter = query.unique();                                                         
 452                                                                                                          
 453             if (notificationFilter == null) {                                                            
 454                 LOG.debug("No Notification Filter found");                                               
 455                 return true;                                                                             
 456             }                                                                                            
 457                                                                                                          
 458             LOG.debug("Loaded notification filter for '{}'", packageName);                               
 459             Query<NotificationFilterEntry> queryEntries = notificationFilterEntryDao.queryBuilder().where🔵
 460                                                                                                          
 461             List<NotificationFilterEntry> filterEntries = queryEntries.list();                           
 462                                                                                                          
 463             if (BuildConfig.DEBUG) {                                                                     
 464                 LOG.info("Database lookup took '{}' ms", System.currentTimeMillis() - start);            
 465             }                                                                                            
 466                                                                                                          
 467             if (!filterEntries.isEmpty()) {                                                              
 468                 for (NotificationFilterEntry temp : filterEntries) {                                     
 469                     wordsList.add(temp.getNotificationFilterContent());                                  
 470                     LOG.debug("Loaded filter word: " + temp.getNotificationFilterContent());             
 471                 }                                                                                        
 472             }                                                                                            
 473                                                                                                          
 474         } catch (Exception e) {                                                                          
 475             LOG.error("Could not acquire DB.", e);                                                       
 476             return true;                                                                                 
 477         }                                                                                                
 478                                                                                                          
 479         return shouldContinueAfterFilter(body, wordsList, notificationFilter);                           
 480     }

 482     private void handleCallNotification(StatusBarNotification sbn) {                                     
 483         String app = sbn.getPackageName();                                                               
 484         LOG.debug("got call from: " + app);                                                              
 485         if (app.equals("com.android.dialer")) {                                                          
 486             LOG.debug("Ignoring non-voip call");                                                         
 487             return;                                                                                      
 488         }                                                                                                
 489         Notification noti = sbn.getNotification();                                                       
 490         dumpExtras(noti.extras);                                                                         
 491         boolean callStarted = false;                                                                     
 492         if ((noti.actions != null) && (noti.actions.length > 0)) {                                       
 493             for (Notification.Action action : noti.actions) {                                            
 494                 LOG.info("Found call action: " + action.title);                                          
 495             }                                                                                            
 496             if (noti.actions.length == 1) {                                                              
 497                 if (mLastCallCommand == CallSpec.CALL_INCOMING) {                                        
 498                     LOG.info("There is only one call action and previous state was CALL_INCOMING, assumin🔵
 499                     callStarted = true;                                                                  
 500                 } else {                                                                                 
 501                     LOG.info("There is only one call action and previous state was not CALL_INCOMING, ass🔵
 502                     // FIXME: is there a way to detect transition CALL_OUTGOING -> CALL_START for more co🔵
 503                     return;                                                                              
 504                 }                                                                                        
 505             }                                                                                            
 506             /*try {                                                                                      
 507                 LOG.info("Executing first action");                                                      
 508                 noti.actions[0].actionIntent.send();                                                     
 509             } catch (PendingIntent.CanceledException e) {                                                
 510                 e.printStackTrace();                                                                     
 511             }*/                                                                                          
 512         }                                                                                                
 513         // figure out sender                                                                             
 514         String number;                                                                                   
 515         if (noti.extras.containsKey(Notification.EXTRA_PEOPLE)) {                                        
 516             number = noti.extras.getString(Notification.EXTRA_PEOPLE);                                   
 517         } else if (noti.extras.containsKey(Notification.EXTRA_TITLE)) {                                  
 518             number = noti.extras.getString(Notification.EXTRA_TITLE);                                    
 519         } else {                                                                                         
 520             String appName = getAppName(app);                                                            
 521             number = (appName != null) ? appName : app;                                                  
 522         }                                                                                                
 523         activeCallPostTime = sbn.getPostTime();                                                          
 524         CallSpec callSpec = new CallSpec();                                                              
 525         callSpec.number = number;                                                                        
 526         callSpec.command = (callStarted) ? CallSpec.CALL_START : CallSpec.CALL_INCOMING;                 
 527         mLastCallCommand = callSpec.command;                                                             
 528         GBApplication.deviceService().onSetCallState(callSpec);                                          
 529     }

 531     boolean shouldContinueAfterFilter(@NonNull String body, @NonNull List<String> wordsList, @NonNull Not🔵
 532                                                                                                          
 533         LOG.debug("Mode: '{}' Submode: '{}' WordsList: '{}'", notificationFilter.getNotificationFilterMod🔵
 534                                                                                                          
 535         boolean allMode = notificationFilter.getNotificationFilterSubMode() == NOTIFICATION_FILTER_SUBMOD🔵
 536                                                                                                          
 537         switch (notificationFilter.getNotificationFilterMode()) {                                        
 538             case NOTIFICATION_FILTER_MODE_BLACKLIST:                                                     
 539                 if (allMode) {                                                                           
 540                     for (String word : wordsList) {                                                      
 541                         if (!body.contains(word)) {                                                      
 542                             LOG.info("Not every word was found, blacklist has no effect, processing conti🔵
 543                             return true;                                                                 
 544                         }                                                                                
 545                     }                                                                                    
 546                     LOG.info("Every word was found, blacklist has effect, processing stops.");           
 547                     return false;                                                                        
 548                 } else {                                                                                 
 549                     boolean containsAny = StringUtils.containsAny(body, wordsList.toArray(new CharSequenc🔵
 550                     if (!containsAny) {                                                                  
 551                         LOG.info("No matching word was found, blacklist has no effect, processing continu🔵
 552                     } else {                                                                             
 553                         LOG.info("At least one matching word was found, blacklist has effect, processing 🔵
 554                     }                                                                                    
 555                     return !containsAny;                                                                 
 556                 }                                                                                        
 557                                                                                                          
 558             case NOTIFICATION_FILTER_MODE_WHITELIST:                                                     
 559                 if (allMode) {                                                                           
 560                     for (String word : wordsList) {                                                      
 561                         if (!body.contains(word)) {                                                      
 562                             LOG.info("Not every word was found, whitelist has no effect, processing stops🔵
 563                             return false;                                                                
 564                         }                                                                                
 565                     }                                                                                    
 566                     LOG.info("Every word was found, whitelist has effect, processing continues.");       
 567                     return true;                                                                         
 568                 } else {                                                                                 
 569                     boolean containsAny = StringUtils.containsAny(body, wordsList.toArray(new CharSequenc🔵
 570                     if (containsAny) {                                                                   
 571                         LOG.info("At least one matching word was found, whitelist has effect, processing 🔵
 572                     } else {                                                                             
 573                         LOG.info("No matching word was found, whitelist has no effect, processing stops."🔵
 574                     }                                                                                    
 575                     return containsAny;                                                                  
 576                 }                                                                                        
 577                                                                                                          
 578             default:                                                                                     
 579                 return true;                                                                             
 580         }                                                                                                
 581     }

 583     // Strip Unicode control sequences: some apps like Telegram add a lot of them for unknown reasons    
 584     private String sanitizeUnicode(String orig) {                                                        
 585         return orig.replaceAll("\\p{C}", "");                                                            
 586     }                                                                                                    
 587                                                                                                          
 588     private void dissectNotificationTo(Notification notification, NotificationSpec notificationSpec,     
 589                                        boolean preferBigText) {                                          
 590                                                                                                          
 591         Bundle extras = NotificationCompat.getExtras(notification);                                      
 592                                                                                                          
 593         //dumpExtras(extras);                                                                            
 594         if (extras == null) {                                                                            
 595             return;                                                                                      
 596         }                                                                                                
 597                                                                                                          
 598         CharSequence title = extras.getCharSequence(Notification.EXTRA_TITLE);                           
 599         if (title != null) {                                                                             
 600             notificationSpec.title = sanitizeUnicode(title.toString());                                  
 601         }                                                                                                
 602                                                                                                          
 603         CharSequence contentCS = null;                                                                   
 604         if (preferBigText && extras.containsKey(Notification.EXTRA_BIG_TEXT)) {                          
 605             contentCS = extras.getCharSequence(NotificationCompat.EXTRA_BIG_TEXT);                       
 606         } else if (extras.containsKey(Notification.EXTRA_TEXT)) {                                        
 607             contentCS = extras.getCharSequence(NotificationCompat.EXTRA_TEXT);                           
 608         }                                                                                                
 609         if (contentCS != null) {                                                                         
 610             notificationSpec.body = sanitizeUnicode(contentCS.toString());                               
 611         }                                                                                                
 612                                                                                                          
 613     }

 615     private boolean isServiceRunning() {                                                                 
 616         ActivityManager manager = (ActivityManager) getSystemService(ACTIVITY_SERVICE);                  
 617         if (manager == null) {                                                                           
 618             return false;                                                                                
 619         }                                                                                                
 620         for (ActivityManager.RunningServiceInfo service : manager.getRunningServices(Integer.MAX_VALUE)) 🔵
 621             if (DeviceCommunicationService.class.getName().equals(service.service.getClassName())) {     
 622                 return true;                                                                             
 623             }                                                                                            
 624         }                                                                                                
 625         return false;                                                                                    
 626     }

 628     private boolean handleMediaSessionNotification(StatusBarNotification sbn) {                          
 629         MediaSessionCompat.Token mediaSession = getMediaSession(sbn.getNotification());                  
 630         return (mediaSession != null) && handleMediaSessionNotification(mediaSession);                   
 631     }

 633     /**                                                                                                  
 634      * Try to handle media session notifications that tell info about the current play state.            
 635      *                                                                                                   
 636      * @param mediaSession The mediasession to handle.                                                   
 637      * @return true if notification was handled, false otherwise                                         
 638      */                                                                                                  
 639     public boolean handleMediaSessionNotification(MediaSessionCompat.Token mediaSession) {               
 640         MusicSpec musicSpec = new MusicSpec();                                                           
 641         MusicStateSpec stateSpec = new MusicStateSpec();                                                 
 642                                                                                                          
 643         MediaControllerCompat c;                                                                         
 644         try {                                                                                            
 645             c = new MediaControllerCompat(getApplicationContext(), mediaSession);                        
 646                                                                                                          
 647             PlaybackStateCompat s = c.getPlaybackState();                                                
 648             stateSpec.position = (int) (s.getPosition() / 1000);                                         
 649             stateSpec.playRate = Math.round(100 * s.getPlaybackSpeed());                                 
 650             stateSpec.repeat = 1;                                                                        
 651             stateSpec.shuffle = 1;                                                                       
 652             switch (s.getState()) {                                                                      
 653                 case PlaybackStateCompat.STATE_PLAYING:                                                  
 654                     stateSpec.state = MusicStateSpec.STATE_PLAYING;                                      
 655                     break;                                                                               
 656                 case PlaybackStateCompat.STATE_STOPPED:                                                  
 657                     stateSpec.state = MusicStateSpec.STATE_STOPPED;                                      
 658                     break;                                                                               
 659                 case PlaybackStateCompat.STATE_PAUSED:                                                   
 660                     stateSpec.state = MusicStateSpec.STATE_PAUSED;                                       
 661                     break;                                                                               
 662                 default:                                                                                 
 663                     stateSpec.state = MusicStateSpec.STATE_UNKNOWN;                                      
 664                     break;                                                                               
 665             }                                                                                            
 666                                                                                                          
 667             MediaMetadataCompat d = c.getMetadata();                                                     
 668             if (d == null)                                                                               
 669                 return false;                                                                            
 670             if (d.containsKey(MediaMetadata.METADATA_KEY_ARTIST))                                        
 671                 musicSpec.artist = d.getString(MediaMetadataCompat.METADATA_KEY_ARTIST);                 
 672             if (d.containsKey(MediaMetadata.METADATA_KEY_ALBUM))                                         
 673                 musicSpec.album = d.getString(MediaMetadataCompat.METADATA_KEY_ALBUM);                   
 674             if (d.containsKey(MediaMetadata.METADATA_KEY_TITLE))                                         
 675                 musicSpec.track = d.getString(MediaMetadataCompat.METADATA_KEY_TITLE);                   
 676             if (d.containsKey(MediaMetadata.METADATA_KEY_DURATION))                                      
 677                 musicSpec.duration = (int) d.getLong(MediaMetadataCompat.METADATA_KEY_DURATION) / 1000;  
 678             if (d.containsKey(MediaMetadata.METADATA_KEY_NUM_TRACKS))                                    
 679                 musicSpec.trackCount = (int) d.getLong(MediaMetadataCompat.METADATA_KEY_NUM_TRACKS);     
 680             if (d.containsKey(MediaMetadata.METADATA_KEY_TRACK_NUMBER))                                  
 681                 musicSpec.trackNr = (int) d.getLong(MediaMetadataCompat.METADATA_KEY_TRACK_NUMBER);      
 682                                                                                                          
 683             // finally, tell the device about it                                                         
 684             GBApplication.deviceService().onSetMusicInfo(musicSpec);                                     
 685             GBApplication.deviceService().onSetMusicState(stateSpec);                                    
 686                                                                                                          
 687             return true;                                                                                 
 688         } catch (NullPointerException | RemoteException e) {                                             
 689             return false;                                                                                
 690         }                                                                                                
 691     }

 693     @Override                                                                                            
 694     public void onNotificationRemoved(StatusBarNotification sbn) {                                       
 695         logNotification(sbn, false);                                                                     
 696         notificationStack.remove(sbn.getPackageName());                                                  
 697         if (shouldIgnoreNotifications()) {                                                               
 698             return;                                                                                      
 699         }                                                                                                
 700         if (shouldIgnoreSource(sbn)) {                                                                   
 701             return;                                                                                      
 702         }                                                                                                
 703         if (handleMediaSessionNotification(sbn)) {                                                       
 704             return;                                                                                      
 705         }                                                                                                
 706         if (GBApplication.isRunningLollipopOrLater()) {                                                  
 707             if (Notification.CATEGORY_CALL.equals(sbn.getNotification().category) && (activeCallPostTime 🔵
 708                 activeCallPostTime = 0;                                                                  
 709                 CallSpec callSpec = new CallSpec();                                                      
 710                 callSpec.command = CallSpec.CALL_END;                                                    
 711                 mLastCallCommand = callSpec.command;                                                     
 712                 GBApplication.deviceService().onSetCallState(callSpec);                                  
 713             }                                                                                            
 714         }                                                                                                
 715         // FIXME: DISABLED for now                                                                       
 716         if (shouldIgnoreNotification(sbn)) {                                                             
 717             return;                                                                                      
 718         }                                                                                                
 719         Prefs prefs = GBApplication.getPrefs();                                                          
 720         if (prefs.getBoolean("autoremove_notifications", true)) {                                        
 721             LOG.info("notification removed, will ask device to delete it");                              
 722             GBApplication.deviceService().onDeleteNotification(((int) (sbn.getPostTime())));             
 723         }                                                                                                
 724     }

 744     private boolean shouldIgnoreNotifications() {                                                        
 745         /*                                                                                               
 746          * return early if DeviceCommunicationService is not running,                                    
 747          * else the service would get started every time we get a notification.                          
 748          * unfortunately we cannot enable/disable NotificationListener at runtime like we do with        
 749          * broadcast receivers because it seems to invalidate the permissions that are                   
 750          * necessary for NotificationListenerService                                                     
 751          */                                                                                              
 752         if (!isServiceRunning()) {                                                                       
 753             LOG.trace("Service is not running, ignoring notification");                                  
 754             return true;                                                                                 
 755         }                                                                                                
 756         return false;                                                                                    
 757     }

 759     private boolean shouldIgnoreSource(StatusBarNotification sbn) {                                      
 760         String source = sbn.getPackageName();                                                            
 761         Prefs prefs = GBApplication.getPrefs();                                                          
 762         /* do not display messages from "android"                                                        
 763          * This includes keyboard selection message, usb connection messages, etc                        
 764          * Hope it does not filter out too much, we will see...                                          
 765          */                                                                                              
 766         if (((source.equals("android") || source.equals("com.android.systemui")) || source.equals("com.an🔵
 767             LOG.info("Ignoring notification, is a system event");                                        
 768             return true;                                                                                 
 769         }                                                                                                
 770         if ((((source.equals("com.moez.QKSMS") || source.equals("com.android.mms")) || source.equals("com🔵
 771             if (!"never".equals(prefs.getString("notification_mode_sms", "when_screen_off"))) {          
 772                 return true;                                                                             
 773             }                                                                                            
 774         }                                                                                                
 775         if (GBApplication.appIsNotifBlacklisted(source)) {                                               
 776             LOG.info("Ignoring notification, application is blacklisted");                               
 777             return true;                                                                                 
 778         }                                                                                                
 779         return false;                                                                                    
 780     }

 782     private boolean shouldIgnoreNotification(StatusBarNotification sbn) {                                
 783         Notification notification = sbn.getNotification();                                               
 784         String source = sbn.getPackageName();                                                            
 785         NotificationType type = AppNotificationType.getInstance().get(source);                           
 786         //ignore notifications marked as LocalOnly https://developer.android.com/reference/android/app/No🔵
 787         //some Apps always mark their notifcations as read-only                                          
 788         if (((NotificationCompat.getLocalOnly(notification) && (type != NotificationType.WECHAT)) && (typ🔵
 789             // see https://github.com/Freeyourgadget/Gadgetbridge/issues/1109                            
 790             LOG.info("local only");                                                                      
 791             return true;                                                                                 
 792         }                                                                                                
 793         Prefs prefs = GBApplication.getPrefs();                                                          
 794         if (!prefs.getBoolean("notifications_generic_whenscreenon", false)) {                            
 795             PowerManager powermanager = ((PowerManager) (getSystemService(POWER_SERVICE)));              
 796             if ((powermanager != null) && powermanager.isScreenOn()) {                                   
 797                 // LOG.info("Not forwarding notification, screen seems to be on and settings do not allow🔵
 798                 return true;                                                                             
 799             }                                                                                            
 800         }                                                                                                
 801         return (notification.flags & Notification.FLAG_ONGOING_EVENT) == Notification.FLAG_ONGOING_EVENT;
 802     }

 804     /**                                                                                                  
 805      * Get the notification color that should be used for this Pebble notification.                      
 806      *                                                                                                   
 807      * Note that this method will *not* edit the NotificationSpec passed in. It will only evaluate the Pe🔵
 808      *                                                                                                   
 809      * See Issue #815 on GitHub to see how notification colors are set.                                  
 810      *                                                                                                   
 811      * @param notificationSpec The NotificationSpec to read from.                                        
 812      * @return Returns a PebbleColor that best represents this notification.                             
 813      */                                                                                                  
 814     private byte getPebbleColorForNotification(NotificationSpec notificationSpec) {                      
 815         String appId = notificationSpec.sourceAppId;                                                     
 816         NotificationType existingType = notificationSpec.type;                                           
 817                                                                                                          
 818         // If the notification type is known, return the associated color.                               
 819         if (existingType != NotificationType.UNKNOWN) {                                                  
 820             return existingType.color;                                                                   
 821         }                                                                                                
 822                                                                                                          
 823         // Otherwise, we go and attempt to find the color from the app icon.                             
 824         Drawable icon;                                                                                   
 825         try {                                                                                            
 826             icon = getApplicationContext().getPackageManager().getApplicationIcon(appId);                
 827             Objects.requireNonNull(icon);                                                                
 828         } catch (Exception ex) {                                                                         
 829             // If we can't get the icon, we go with the default defined above.                           
 830             LOG.warn("Could not get icon for AppID " + appId, ex);                                       
 831             return PebbleColor.IslamicGreen;                                                             
 832         }                                                                                                
 833                                                                                                          
 834         Bitmap bitmapIcon = BitmapUtil.convertDrawableToBitmap(icon);                                    
 835         int iconPrimaryColor = new Palette.Builder(bitmapIcon)                                           
 836                 .generate()                                                                              
 837                 .getVibrantColor(Color.parseColor("#aa0000"));                                           
 838                                                                                                          
 839         return PebbleUtils.getPebbleColor(iconPrimaryColor);                                             
 840     }

 116      private final BroadcastReceiver mReceiver = new BroadcastReceiver() {                                         
 117                                                                                                                    
 118          @Override                                                                                                 
 119          public void onReceive(Context context, Intent intent) {                                                   
 120              String action = intent.getAction();                                                                   
 121              if (action == null) {                                                                                 
 122                  LOG.warn("no action");                                                                            
 123                  return;                                                                                           
 124              }                                                                                                     
 125                                                                                                                    
 126              int handle = (int) intent.getLongExtra("handle", -1);                                                 
 127              switch (action) {                                                                                     
 128                  case GBApplication.ACTION_QUIT:                                                                   
 129                      stopSelf();                                                                                   
 130                      break;                                                                                        
 131                                                                                                                    
 132                  case ACTION_OPEN: {                                                                               
 133                      StatusBarNotification[] sbns = NotificationListener.this.getActiveNotifications();            
 134                      Long ts = (Long) mNotificationHandleLookup.lookup(handle);                                    
 135                      if (ts == null) {                                                                             
 136                          LOG.info("could not lookup handle for open action");                                      
 137                          break;                                                                                    
 138                      }                                                                                             
 139                                                                                                                    
 140                      for (StatusBarNotification sbn : sbns) {                                                      
 141                          if (sbn.getPostTime() == ts) {                                                            
 142                              try {                                                                                 
 143                                  PendingIntent pi = sbn.getNotification().contentIntent;                           
 144                                  if (pi != null) {                                                                 
 145                                      pi.send();                                                                    
 146                                  }                                                                                 
 147                              } catch (PendingIntent.CanceledException e) {                                         
 148                                  e.printStackTrace();                                                              
 149                              }                                                                                     
 150                          }                                                                                         
 151                      }                                                                                             
 152                      break;                                                                                        
 153                  }                                                                                                 
 154                  case ACTION_MUTE:                                                                                 
 155                      String packageName = (String) mPackageLookup.lookup(handle);                                  
 156                      if (packageName == null) {                                                                    
 157                          LOG.info("could not lookup handle for mute action");                                      
 158                          break;                                                                                    
 159                      }                                                                                             
 160                                                                                                                    
 161                      LOG.info("going to mute " + packageName);                                                     
 162                      GBApplication.addAppToNotifBlacklist(packageName);                                            
 163                      break;                                                                                        
 164                  case ACTION_DISMISS: {                                                                            
 165                      StatusBarNotification[] sbns = NotificationListener.this.getActiveNotifications();            
 166                      Long ts = (Long) mNotificationHandleLookup.lookup(handle);                                    
 167                      if (ts == null) {                                                                             
 168                          LOG.info("could not lookup handle for dismiss action");                                   
 169                          break;                                                                                    
 170                      }                                                                                             
 171                      for (StatusBarNotification sbn : sbns) {                                                      
 172                          if (sbn.getPostTime() == ts) {                                                            
 173                              if (GBApplication.isRunningLollipopOrLater()) {                                       
 174                                  String key = sbn.getKey();                                                        
 175                                  NotificationListener.this.cancelNotification(key);                                
 176                              } else {                                                                              
 177                                  int id = sbn.getId();                                                             
 178                                  String pkg = sbn.getPackageName();                                                
 179                                  String tag = sbn.getTag();                                                        
 180                                  NotificationListener.this.cancelNotification(pkg, tag, id);                       
 181                              }                                                                                     
 182                          }                                                                                         
 183                      }                                                                                             
 184                      break;                                                                                        
 185                  }                                                                                                 
 186                  case ACTION_DISMISS_ALL:                                                                          
 187                      NotificationListener.this.cancelAllNotifications();                                           
 188                      break;                                                                                        
 189                  case ACTION_REPLY:                                                                                
 190                      NotificationCompat.Action wearableAction = (NotificationCompat.Action) mActionLookup.lookup(ha🔵
 191                      String reply = intent.getStringExtra("reply");                                                
 192                      if (wearableAction != null) {                                                                 
 193                          PendingIntent actionIntent = wearableAction.getActionIntent();                            
 194                          Intent localIntent = new Intent();                                                        
 195                          localIntent.addFlags(Intent.FLAG_ACTIVITY_NEW_TASK);                                      
 196                          if(wearableAction.getRemoteInputs()!=null) {                                              
 197                              RemoteInput[] remoteInputs = wearableAction.getRemoteInputs();                        
 198                              Bundle extras = new Bundle();                                                         
 199                              extras.putCharSequence(remoteInputs[0].getResultKey(), reply);                        
 200                              RemoteInput.addResultsToIntent(remoteInputs, localIntent, extras);                    
 201                          }                                                                                         
 202                          try {                                                                                     
 203                              LOG.info("will send exec intent to remote application");                              
 204                              actionIntent.send(context, 0, localIntent);                                           
 205                              mActionLookup.remove(handle);                                                         
 206                          } catch (PendingIntent.CanceledException e) {                                             
 207                              LOG.warn("replyToLastNotification error: " + e.getLocalizedMessage());                
 208                          }                                                                                         
 209                      }

 404      private boolean checkNotificationContentForWhiteAndBlackList(String packageName, String body) {               
 405          long start = System.currentTimeMillis();                                                                  
 406                                                                                                                    
 407          List<String> wordsList = new ArrayList<>();                                                               
 408          NotificationFilter notificationFilter;                                                                    
 409                                                                                                                    
 410          try (DBHandler db = GBApplication.acquireDB()) {                                                          
 411                                                                                                                    
 412              NotificationFilterDao notificationFilterDao = db.getDaoSession().getNotificationFilterDao();          
 413              NotificationFilterEntryDao notificationFilterEntryDao = db.getDaoSession().getNotificationFilterEntryD🔵
 414                                                                                                                    
 415              Query<NotificationFilter> query = notificationFilterDao.queryBuilder().where(NotificationFilterDao.Pro🔵
 416              notificationFilter = query.unique();                                                                  
 417                                                                                                                    
 418              if (notificationFilter == null) {                                                                     
 419                  LOG.debug("No Notification Filter found");                                                        
 420                  return true;                                                                                      
 421              }                                                                                                     
 422                                                                                                                    
 423              LOG.debug("Loaded notification filter for '{}'", packageName);                                        
 424              Query<NotificationFilterEntry> queryEntries = notificationFilterEntryDao.queryBuilder().where(Notifica🔵
 425                                                                                                                    
 426              List<NotificationFilterEntry> filterEntries = queryEntries.list();                                    
 427                                                                                                                    
 428              if (BuildConfig.DEBUG) {                                                                              
 429                  LOG.info("Database lookup took '{}' ms", System.currentTimeMillis() - start);                     
 430              }                                                                                                     
 431                                                                                                                    
 432              if (!filterEntries.isEmpty()) {                                                                       
 433                  for (NotificationFilterEntry temp : filterEntries) {                                              
 434                      wordsList.add(temp.getNotificationFilterContent());                                           
 435                      LOG.debug("Loaded filter word: " + temp.getNotificationFilterContent());                      
 436                  }                                                                                                 
 437              }                                                                                                     
 438                                                                                                                    
 439          } catch (Exception e) {                                                                                   
 440              LOG.error("Could not acquire DB.", e);                                                                
 441              return true;                                                                                          
 442          }                                                                                                         
 443                                                                                                                    
 444          return shouldContinueAfterFilter(body, wordsList, notificationFilter);                                    
 445      }

 447      private void handleCallNotification(StatusBarNotification sbn) {                                              
 448          String app = sbn.getPackageName();                                                                        
 449          LOG.debug("got call from: " + app);                                                                       
 450          if(app.equals("com.android.dialer")) {                                                                    
 451              LOG.debug("Ignoring non-voip call");                                                                  
 452              return;                                                                                               
 453          }                                                                                                         
 454          Notification noti = sbn.getNotification();                                                                
 455          dumpExtras(noti.extras);                                                                                  

 456          if(noti.actions != null && noti.actions.length > 0) {                                                     
 457              for (Notification.Action action : noti.actions) {                                                     
 458                  LOG.info("Found call action: " + action.title);                                                   










 459              }                                                                                                     
 460              /*try {                                                                                               
 461                  LOG.info("Executing first action");                                                               
 462                  noti.actions[0].actionIntent.send();                                                              
 463              } catch (PendingIntent.CanceledException e) {                                                         
 464                  e.printStackTrace();                                                                              
 465              }*/                                                                                                   
 466          }                                                                                                         
 467                                                                                                                    
 468          // figure out sender                                                                                      
 469          String number;                                                                                            
 470          if(noti.extras.containsKey(Notification.EXTRA_PEOPLE)) {                                                  
 471              number = noti.extras.getString(Notification.EXTRA_PEOPLE);                                            
 472          } else if(noti.extras.containsKey(Notification.EXTRA_TITLE)) {                                            
 473              number = noti.extras.getString(Notification.EXTRA_TITLE);                                             
 474          } else {                                                                                                  
 475              String appName = getAppName(app);                                                                     
 476              number = appName != null ? appName : app;                                                             
 477          }                                                                                                         
 478          activeCallPostTime = sbn.getPostTime();                                                                   
 479          CallSpec callSpec = new CallSpec();                                                                       
 480          callSpec.number = number;                                                                                 
 481          callSpec.command = CallSpec.CALL_INCOMING;                                                                


 482          GBApplication.deviceService().onSetCallState(callSpec);                                                   
 483      }

 485      boolean shouldContinueAfterFilter(@NonNull String body, @NonNull List<String> wordsList, @NonNull Notification🔵
 486                                                                                                                    
 487          LOG.debug("Mode: '{}' Submode: '{}' WordsList: '{}'", notificationFilter.getNotificationFilterMode(), noti🔵
 488                                                                                                                    
 489          boolean allMode = notificationFilter.getNotificationFilterSubMode() == NOTIFICATION_FILTER_SUBMODE_ALL;   
 490                                                                                                                    
 491          switch (notificationFilter.getNotificationFilterMode()) {                                                 
 492              case NOTIFICATION_FILTER_MODE_BLACKLIST:                                                              
 493                  if (allMode) {                                                                                    
 494                      for (String word : wordsList) {                                                               
 495                          if (!body.contains(word)) {                                                               
 496                              LOG.info("Not every word was found, blacklist has no effect, processing continues."); 
 497                              return true;                                                                          
 498                          }                                                                                         
 499                      }                                                                                             
 500                      LOG.info("Every word was found, blacklist has effect, processing stops.");                    
 501                      return false;                                                                                 
 502                  } else {                                                                                          
 503                      boolean containsAny = StringUtils.containsAny(body, wordsList.toArray(new CharSequence[0]));  
 504                      if (!containsAny) {                                                                           
 505                          LOG.info("No matching word was found, blacklist has no effect, processing continues.");   
 506                      } else {                                                                                      
 507                          LOG.info("At least one matching word was found, blacklist has effect, processing stops.");
 508                      }                                                                                             
 509                      return !containsAny;                                                                          
 510                  }                                                                                                 
 511                                                                                                                    
 512              case NOTIFICATION_FILTER_MODE_WHITELIST:                                                              
 513                  if (allMode) {                                                                                    
 514                      for (String word : wordsList) {                                                               
 515                          if (!body.contains(word)) {                                                               
 516                              LOG.info("Not every word was found, whitelist has no effect, processing stops.");     
 517                              return false;                                                                         
 518                          }                                                                                         
 519                      }                                                                                             
 520                      LOG.info("Every word was found, whitelist has effect, processing continues.");                
 521                      return true;                                                                                  
 522                  } else {                                                                                          
 523                      boolean containsAny = StringUtils.containsAny(body, wordsList.toArray(new CharSequence[0]));  
 524                      if (containsAny) {                                                                            
 525                          LOG.info("At least one matching word was found, whitelist has effect, processing continues🔵
 526                      } else {                                                                                      
 527                          LOG.info("No matching word was found, whitelist has no effect, processing stops.");       
 528                      }                                                                                             
 529                      return containsAny;                                                                           
 530                  }                                                                                                 
 531                                                                                                                    
 532              default:                                                                                              
 533                  return true;                                                                                      
 534          }                                                                                                         
 535      }
